Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.12,0:25:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}请告诉我们你和巴兹的关系\NWould you tell us the nature of your relationship with Mr. Boz?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.35,0:25:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我和他大约有一年半的性交往\NI had sex with him for about a year and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.59,0:25:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我喜欢和他性交\NI liked having sex with him.
