Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.45,0:33:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}或许书中所说的都会实现\NMaybe all her books come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.49,0:33:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她的父母死于意外. 我也不在乎她还写了什么事\NHer parents died in an accident. I don't care what else she published.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.56,0:33:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你想叫我作书评吗？\NWhat are you,a book critic?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.69,0:33:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他们怎么死的？你们调查过吗？\NHow'd they die? Was there an investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.10,0:33:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你是说他先杀了自己父母， 然后杀了曼尼瓦斯卡？\NYou're saying she killed her parents? Did she kill Manny Vasquez too?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.57,0:33:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}难道她一上床就会突然变成一个杀人狂\NNot unless she climbed into the ring and turned into one mean son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.87,0:33:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}或许她学会用一招左钩拳\NMaybe she did. Maybe she grew herself an afro...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.18,0:33:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}用鞋油涂在脸上假装拳王\Ndeveloped a hell of a left hook and put shoe polish all over her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.81,0:33:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-让我们再替她测验一次. -去你妈的\N- Let's polygraph her again. - Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.51,0:33:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}也去你妈的\NFuck you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.85,0:33:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}别担心，尼克自己会去干\NDon't worry,Phil. Nick'll fuck himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.39,0:34:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你们的笑话很好笑. 杰克，再给我一杯双份的\NYou guys are very funny. Hey,Chuckie,get me another double.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.42,0:34:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}嘿！开枪的\NHey,shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.83,0:34:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你又酗酒了\NAre you back on the blackjack,shooter?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.79,0:34:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-我们正在讨论你的案子. -我知道，我也不怀疑\N- We're discussing a case here. - I know that. I have no doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.57,0:34:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}尼克，你的酒\NHere you go,Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.50,0:34:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}双份的？\NA double,huh,shooter?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.18,0:34:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我已经下班了\NI'm off duty,Nilsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.45,0:34:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}听到了吗？我下班了， 正在讨论这件案子\NYou hear me? I'm off duty discussing a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.72,0:34:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你有什么问题吗？\NNow,I.A. Shouldn't have a problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.42,0:34:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}或许我该申请加班费\NMaybe I should put in for some overtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.73,0:34:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}工作别太卖力. 会使你酗酒\NDon't work too hard,shooter. It might drive you to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.40,0:34:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}老子我爽，你闪一边去！\NStop riding me,man! I'll kick your fucking teeth in!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.74,0:34:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-怎么回事？ -没什么事，大夫\N- What's the problem? - No problem,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.51,0:34:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}精神病医生来了， 及时来解救她心爱的病人\NHere comes the shrink,just in time to save her favorite patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.61,0:34:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}滚一边去，马提！\NJust fuck off,Marty!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.68,0:35:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你们今晚可以好好爽一下\NYou kids have a good time tonight,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.16,0:35:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-他自找的. -没错！别上他的当\N- He's asking for it. - That's right,so don't take the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.20,0:35:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}想走吗？\NDo you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.60,0:35:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-是的. -我们走\N- Yes. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.67,0:35:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}有时候我觉的他勾上她 只是为了摆脱风纪组\NSometimes I think he started banging her just to get Internal Affairs off him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.64,0:35:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}那倒不尽然. 他是认真的\NHe ain't that way. He's got a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.88,0:37:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她人怎么样？\NWhat was she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.21,0:37:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-谁？ -凯瑟琳楚梅\N- Who? - Catherine Tramell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.09,0:37:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}确定是她. 但她的书提供了藉口\NYou had her pegged. She used her book as an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.86,0:37:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我在柏克莱见过她\NI met her at Berkeley.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.53,0:38:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我们同样选修某些课程\NWe were in some of the same classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.23,0:38:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你为何不早告诉我？\NWhy didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.90,0:38:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我现在告诉你了\NI'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.58,0:38:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你从未这个样子，为什么？\NYou've never been like that before. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.55,0:38:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你说呢，你是心理医生\NYou tell me. You're the shrink.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.89,0:38:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-你不是在跟我作爱. -那我是在跟谁作爱？\N- You weren't making love to me. - Who was I making love to?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.39,0:38:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你根本不是在作爱\NYou weren't making love.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.30,0:38:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我想抽支烟\NI need a cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.80,0:38:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你说你已经戒了\NI thought you said you quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.18,0:38:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}在最上层抽屉里\NIt's the top drawer in the foyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.18,0:38:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}出去时顺便带着！\NGet it on your way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.12,0:39:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-开始了吗？ -在等你\N- Have you started? - Waitin' on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.76,0:39:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-你看起来糟透了. -不是，他刚作过心理分析\N- You look like dog shit. - No,he looks a little shrunk is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.20,0:39:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}不光是脑袋\NAnd not just in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.70,0:39:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我打电话和柏克莱联络\NAll right,I made a couple of calls to Berkeley.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.37,0:39:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}八九年有位教授曾被谋杀\NThere was a murder in '80. A professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.17,0:39:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}在床上被刺的浑身是洞， 冰锥刺的\NIn his bed,multiple stab wounds, with an ice pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.14,0:39:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}当时楚梅在学校\NTramell was there then, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.65,0:39:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}学校记录说是的\NUniversity records say she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.18,0:39:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}好吧！咱们开始进行. 加斯，你去柏克莱\NOkay,let's move on this. Gus,get out to Berkeley.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.85,0:39:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你去找她其他写的书\NHarrigan,find out what else she's published.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.12,0:39:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你拿她父母死亡档案给我看\NAndrews,get me that file on the parents' accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.76,0:39:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}把贝丝心理分析资料拿一份来\NCopy Beth on everything. I want psychological input.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.69,0:39:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-我呢？ -你已经有一份心理分析资料了\N- What about me? - You're already getting input.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.13,0:39:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你去冲个冷水澡\NYou go soak your head in a tub of ice water.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.71,0:39:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你去追查她的行踪\NYou see where she leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.28,0:43:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}周末愉快\NYou have a good weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.42,0:43:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你也是\NYou too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.15,0:43:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}小心开车\NDrive carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.55,0:43:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-我会的. -再见\N- I will. - Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.12,0:43:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我会给你电话的\NI'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.60,0:45:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你闲着没别的事干 竟然来办公室和电脑打手枪\NAin't you got nothing better to do than to jack off the damn machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.57,0:45:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你来干嘛？\NWhat are you doing here,cowboy?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.44,0:45:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我也来和电脑打手枪\NI came in here to jack off the damn machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.57,0:46:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}一个心理学教授死亡\NOne dead psychology professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.31,0:46:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}高斯丁博士. 你猜怎么样？\NDr. Noah Goldstein. And guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.41,0:46:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他是她的指导教授\NHe was her counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.32,0:46:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她有嫌疑吗？\NWas she a suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.59,0:46:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}没有，根本没叫她问话\NNo,sir. They never even got a statement from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.76,0:46:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}艾索达普金斯？\NHazel Dobkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.43,0:46:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}认识她吗？\NDo you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.33,0:46:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}这么多年都忘不掉\NCouldn't get it out of my head for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.73,0:46:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}三个孩子的贤妻良母\NNice little housewife. Three little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.57,0:46:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}有一个顾家的好丈夫， 也没有财务问题\NNice husband wasn't porking around. No financial problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.37,0:46:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}一个晴朗的日子里 她把全家人都做了\NOne day,out of the clear blue sky, she does them,all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.24,0:46:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}拿了一把结婚礼物收到的刀\NUsed a knife she got for a wedding present.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.38,0:46:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}事后也不否认. 笑得很甜美\NDidn't even deny it. Sweet as honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.68,0:46:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她也说不出原因\NSaid she didn't know why she'd done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.33,0:46:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}吵到你了吗？\N- Hi. - Am I disturbing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.40,0:47:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}没有，请进\NNo,come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.47,0:47:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}咱们上楼去\NLet's go upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.42,0:47:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我把你当作我书中的探长\NI'm using you for my detective in my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.59,0:47:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}不介意吧？\NYou don't mind,do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.43,0:47:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我正在调酒\NI was just gonna make myself a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.43,0:47:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-想喝一点吗？ -不用，谢了\N- Do you want one? - No,thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.50,0:47:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你也戒酒了吗？\NOh,right. You're off the Jack Daniels too,aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.21,0:47:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}有几个问题请教一下\NI've got a few more questions to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.35,0:47:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我也正想问你. 为了我的书\NI have some for you too. For my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.43,0:48:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你对冰块很不满吗？\NDo you have something against ice cubes?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.53,0:48:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我喜欢粗糙的棱角\NI like rough edges.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.56,0:48:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你想问我什么？\NSo,what did you want to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.60,0:48:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}杀人的滋味如何？\NHow does it feel to kill someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.77,0:48:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你来告诉我\NYou tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.38,0:48:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我不知道，你该知道\NI don't know, but you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.55,0:48:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}那是一次意外\NIt was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.48,0:48:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我的枪忽然走火\NThey got in the line of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.69,0:48:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}五年中的4次都是意外？\NFour shootings in five years, all accidents?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.36,0:48:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他们都是毒贩，我当时在卧底\NThey were drug buys. I was working undercover.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.30,0:48:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}想谈谈高斯丁教授的事吗？\NYou want to tell me about Professor Goldstein?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.84,0:48:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}那是老掉牙的人物了\NWell,there's a name from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.54,0:48:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}现代也有个艾索达普金斯\NYou want a name from the present? What about Hazel Dobkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.54,0:48:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}高斯丁是我一年纪的指导教授\NNoah Goldstein was my counselor my freshman year.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.45,0:48:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我的冰锥灵感大概就由此而来 在我书中\NThat's probably where I got the idea for the ice pick for my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.75,0:49:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}潜意识的力量真是惊人\NFunny how the subconscious works.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.32,0:49:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}的确\NHilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.79,0:49:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-艾索是我的朋友. -你的朋友把一家人全宰了\N- Hazel's my friend. - Your friend took out her whole family.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.80,0:49:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她使我了解杀人的冲动\NYes,she helped me understand homicidal impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.30,0:49:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你在学校就学到了\NI thought you would have learned that at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.67,0:49:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}只是理论上的\NOnly in theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.67,0:49:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你对杀人冲动了解十分透彻. 不是吗，枪手？\NBut you know all about homicidal impulse,don't you,shooter?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.48,0:49:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}不是理论，是实务的\NNot in theory,in practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.25,0:49:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}卷入其中的滋味如何？\NWhat happened? Did you get sucked into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.75,0:49:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你无法自拔吗？\NDid you like it too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.52,0:49:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我不知道你在说什么\NI don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.30,0:49:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}谈谈可卡因吧，尼克\NTell me about the coke,Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.80,0:49:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你杀了观光客的那天…\NThe day you shot those two tourists...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.84,0:49:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你吸了多少可卡因？\Nhow much coke did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.58,0:49:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你可以告诉我\NCome on,you can tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.75,0:50:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-我吸了. -你吸了…\N- I didn't. - Yes,you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.66,0:50:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他们没替你检验\NThey never tested you,did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.13,0:50:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}风纪组的人知道\NInternal Affairs knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.13,0:50:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你老婆也知道，对不对？\NYour wife knew too,didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.51,0:50:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她知道怎么回事\NShe knew what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.64,0:50:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你离火焰太近了\NI think you got too close to the flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.62,0:50:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我想你很喜欢\NI think you liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.33,0:50:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}所以她才自杀\NThat's why she killed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.38,0:51:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}嗨，海伦\NHi,hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.42,0:51:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你们两位见过面\NYou two have met,haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.46,0:51:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你会是位了不起的角色\NYou're gonna make a terrific character,Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.71,0:51:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她正在打电话，马上会叫你\NShe's on the phone. She'll be right with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.68,0:51:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-我马上会打回去给你. -探长，你不能进去--\N- I'm gonna have to call you back. - Detective,you can't go in...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.38,0:51:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-谁动过我的档案？ -你在说什么？\N- Who's got access to my file? - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.79,0:51:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}谁动过我那些档案？\NWho has access to my goddamn file?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.16,0:51:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}没人动过. 那些是机密的个人心理资料\NNobody. It's a confidential psychiatric record. It would be illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.86,0:51:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你干的，少对我扯谎言\NDon't you fucking lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.63,0:51:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是风纪组动的\NIt was Internal Affairs,wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.70,0:51:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}不是的\NNo,please.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.80,0:52:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-是谁？ -是尼尔森\N- Who? - It's Nilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.61,0:52:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}有何贵干，柯伦？\NWhat do you want,Curran?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.45,0:52:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你把我的档案卖了\NYou sold her my file,didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.78,0:52:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你在说谁？\NWho are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.09,0:52:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}凯瑟琳楚梅. 她付你多少？\NCatherine Tramell. How much did she pay you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.59,0:52:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}快点住手\NHey,Curran,come on! Damn it,stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.19,0:52:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}多少钱？\NHow much?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.63,0:52:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}快住手，柯伦！\NHey,back off! Back off,Curran!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.53,0:52:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}轻松一点\NNice and easy now. Nice and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.67,0:52:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}去你妈的头，你完蛋了\NYou fucked yourself,shooter. You hear me? You are out!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.67,0:52:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-柯伦，轻松点. -你死定了！\N- Curran,take it easy. - You are out!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.84,0:52:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}省省吧\NSave it,save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.82,0:52:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-尼克，你没事吧？ -我没事\N- What's going down,Hoss? - Nothing. I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.42,0:52:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-他们不会放过你的. -我痛恨被人耍着玩\N- They're gonna want your badge. - I'm tired of being played with.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.59,0:52:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你表现的方式真是与众不同\NYou got a real conclusive way of demonstrating that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.20,0:53:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她把我摸的一清二楚\NShe knows where I live and breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.50,0:53:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我被她盯上了，加斯\NShe's coming after me,Gus.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.27,0:53:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她和你有什么瓜葛？\NWhat is it you got between you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.61,0:53:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-我不知道. -是有点不对\N- I don't know. - Something,though.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.71,0:53:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是的，没错\NSomething.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.46,0:53:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}TV:GeorgeJefferson is unfair. He's short with no hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.90,0:53:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}尼克，你在里面吗？\NNick,are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.91,0:53:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}走开.贝丝，我不想见你\NGo away,Beth. I don't want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.21,0:53:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我还有钥匙\NI still have my key.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.65,0:53:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}放在桌上然后离开\NPut them on the table and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.49,0:54:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}放在他妈的桌上快离开！\NPut them on the goddamn table and leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.19,0:54:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}妈的！别轰我出去. 你欠我的不只是这些\NDamn it! Don't shove me out! You owe me more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.63,0:54:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我什么也不欠你！\NI don't owe you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.33,0:54:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你也不欠我什么\NAnd you don't owe me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.20,0:54:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我们是有上床，大概十到十五次\NWe went to bed,what,10,15 times?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.51,0:54:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}那可不是我的责任\NIt wasn't memorable enough to carry an obligation.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.88,0:54:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}有时候我真的很恨你\NSometimes I really hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.65,0:54:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你为何不替自己开些药方…\NWhy don't you get yourself some friendly little therapist...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.62,0:54:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}让自己温柔一点？\Nto work out some of that hostility?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.09,0:54:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}或许能有些用处\NAnd maybe you can get off once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.16,0:54:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你这神经病\NAre you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.91,0:54:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.68,0:54:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我很少这个样子\NI don't usually act like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.31,0:54:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你怎么把我的档案流出去？\NHow could you give him my file?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.15,0:55:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我是被迫的！\NI had to!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.72,0:55:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他打算将你从局里除名\NHe was going to recommend your discharge from the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.65,0:55:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他也不接受我的评估 认为不够客观\NHe didn't buy my evaluation. He said I wasn't objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.12,0:55:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}所以我拿那个和他作交换条件\NSo I made a deal with him to review the session notes himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.86,0:55:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我没想到他会给别人看\NI didn't think he'd show them to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.33,0:55:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-你是为了我？ -是的\N- You did it for me? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.27,0:55:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}因为我关心你. 才为你这样做\NI care about you. I did it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.21,0:55:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你走吧，拜托你快走\NGo away. Please,just go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.44,0:56:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}喂。\NYo.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.31,0:56:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我马上赶去\NI'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.43,0:57:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}一枪毙命，近距离射击. 大概是点三八左轮\NOne shot. Close range. Probably a.38 caliber revolver.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.30,0:57:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你的枪给我，尼克\NGive me your gun,Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.78,0:57:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你以为--\NYou think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.29,0:57:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我不认为是你. 但我的意见是少数\NI don't,Hoss. But I got the minority opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.83,0:57:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是的，我讨厌他！ 我一时失去控制\NOkay,I went after him! I lost my temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.24,0:57:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你有证据他把你的心理档案 给别人看吗？\NDo you have any evidence that he showed your psychiatric file to anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.21,0:57:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}等一下会找你谈，嘉纳大夫\NWe'll speak with you afterwards,Dr. Garner.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.21,0:57:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-我想参加，不介意吧. -我想你还是--\N- I'd like to sit in. - I'd really rather wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.28,0:57:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我想有她在座应该无所谓， 柯伦探长不反对的话\NIt's all right if Dr. Garner sits in, if Detective Curran doesn't object.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.09,0:58:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-你昨晚人在何处？ -在家看电视\N- Where were you last night? - Home,watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.16,0:58:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}整晚都在？\NAll night?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.53,0:58:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是的，一整晚\NYes,all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.23,0:58:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}在喝酒吗？\NWere you drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.17,0:58:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是的，喝了一点\NYeah,I was drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.84,0:58:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-你何时有开始喝的？ -几天前\N- When did you start drinking again? - A couple of days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.84,0:58:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}大约昨晚十点左右 我看见他在家里\NI saw Detective Curran at his apartment about 10:00 last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.35,0:58:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他当时神智清醒\NHe was sober and lucid.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.32,0:58:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我问他对尼尔森警官的感受\NI asked him,in my capacity as his departmental therapist...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.09,0:58:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我问他对尼尔森警官的感受\Nabout his altercation with Lieutenant Nilsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.29,0:58:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他深表悔意\NHe expressed regret and displayed no hostility.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.52,0:58:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-你在他公寓待了多久？ -大约十五分钟\N- How long were you at his apartment? - About 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.46,0:58:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}直到我放心了才离去\NI saw there was no reason for my concern and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.90,0:58:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}这里不能吸烟的\NThere's no smoking in this building,Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.77,0:58:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你想告我吸烟吗？\NWhat are you gonna do? Charge me with smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.51,0:58:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}天哪--尼克，我再问你一次就够了\NOh,for Christ's... All right,Nick, I'm gonna ask you this just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.28,0:58:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}为了记录，你是否杀了尼尔森？\NFor the record, did you kill Marty Nilsen?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.35,0:58:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.48,0:58:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我不会当着大家的面先诅咒他…\NI'm gonna storm into his office in front of everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.29,0:59:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}然后当晚把他宰了\Nin the middle of the day and kill him that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.29,0:59:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我没那么笨\NI'm not that dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.36,0:59:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你先离去 再回头杀他正好可脱罪. 那是你的不在场证明\NGoing after him before gets you off the hook for killing him. That's your alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.33,0:59:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你也是看书学来的这一套\NLike writing a book about killing a guy gets you off the hook for killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.90,0:59:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}说的好\NGood point.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.10,0:59:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我不懂你在说什么书\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.90,0:59:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-这是我们自己的笑话，混账. -我不觉得好笑\N- A private joke,asshole. - I don't think it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.51,0:59:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你的职务暂时被吊销…\NYou're going on leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.91,0:59:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}继续进行心理状态评估\Npending the outcome of a psychiatric evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.39,0:59:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}贝丝，我马上回来拿行李\NI'll get my stuff in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.46,0:59:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.24,0:59:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我至少能帮上这个忙\NIt's the least I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.40,0:59:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是我害你来问话的\NConsidering I got you into this mess with those reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.27,0:59:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我是说真的，谢谢\NNo,I mean it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.81,1:00:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你怎知道凯瑟琳看过你的档案？\NHow do you know Catherine Tramell saw your file?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.82,1:00:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她知道一些事， 我只告诉过你\NShe knows things about me that I only told you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.52,1:00:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}一定有什么不对\NShe must really be something.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.22,1:00:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}从治疗的观点来看\NFrom a clinical point of view.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.52,1:00:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-她在学校表现如何？ -我跟她不熟\N- What was she like in school? - I hardly knew her.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.46,1:00:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她让我有些毛骨悚然\NShe gave me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.23,1:00:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}不知道为什么\NI don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.33,1:00:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}休息一下.答应我\NGet some rest. Promise?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.21,1:00:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-我昨天说的那些话不是认真的-- -你是的\N- I didn't mean what I said about... - Yes,you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.41,1:00:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我不是小孩子，我会处理的\NI'm a big girl. I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.17,1:01:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-你自己多保重. -你对她父母的调查怎样？\N- You take care of yourself. - What'd you find out about the parents?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.44,1:01:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}别提了\NNo lead,man.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.38,1:01:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你简直是神经病\NYou're on psycho leave. I'm talking to a possible wacko!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.58,1:01:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你知道我神经病，到底怎样？\NYou know I'm wacko. What'd you find out?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.26,1:01:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}游艇爆炸. 燃料箱漏洞\NThe boat blew. There was a leak in the fuel line.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.89,1:01:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}曾经修理过两次 两人投了高额的保险\NThere were two previous repairs and a five mil policy on both of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.90,1:01:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}曾经积极的调查都没结果\NA real heavy investigation but they got zilch.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.30,1:01:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}赔了一大笔钱，说是意外\NBig goose egg. It was an "accident."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.17,1:01:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}风纪组还要找你问话. 由他们调查，我们不插手\NI.A.'s gonna talk to you about Nilsen. They're handling the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.57,1:01:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你和嘉纳大夫保持联络. 对你的评估有帮助\NStay in touch with Dr. Garner. It'll help on the evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.41,1:01:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是她干的\NShe killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.11,1:01:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你说贝丝杀人？\NBeth? Now you've got Beth killing people?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.51,1:01:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是凯瑟琳杀的\NCatherine Tramell. It's part of her game.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.55,1:01:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你先说她偷了你的档案， 现在又说她杀了尼尔森？\NFirst you got her stealing your file, now she's killing Nilsen?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.69,1:01:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}少来这一套，看在老天的份上. 找个地方晒晒太阳\NForget about her! Go somewhere,sit in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.62,1:01:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-让你神智清醒一下！ -你不相信吗？\N- Get her the hell out of your system! - You don't buy it,do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.36,1:01:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她知道没人会相信\NShe knew nobody'd buy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.56,1:01:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她知道没人相信我说的话\NShe knew I'd say she did it and nobody'd buy it!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.13,1:02:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她把你搞得神经错乱！ 离她远一点！\NShe is screwing with your head! Stay away from her!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.76,1:02:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}那件事我听说了\NI heard what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.14,1:02:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你没带枪看来更帅\NWhat good's a shooter without his gun?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.24,1:02:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-你到底发现了什么？ -我有律师\N- How exactly did you find out? - I have attorneys.
