Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.11,1:37:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我写的都是不寻常的人…\NI write about unusual people, and sometimes when I do my research...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.08,1:37:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}有时候为了研究他们必须如此\NI get involved with them.
