Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.26,1:39:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我在学校和她上过一次\NI slept with her once in school.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.10,1:39:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}只是为了好玩. 是为了做实验\NI was just a kid. I was experimenting.
