Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.12,1:40:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你猜她干了什么？\NDo you know what she's doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.98,1:40:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她知道我在伯克莱认识高斯丁\NShe knows I went to Berkeley. She knows I knew Noah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.22,1:40:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她替我编造这些故事\NShe makes up this story about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.22,1:40:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她骗你说有人迷恋她\NShe's handing you somebody who's obsessed with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.93,1:40:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她没骗我 她根本不知道你是谁\NShe didn't hand you to me. She doesn't know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.99,1:40:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她只说是丽莎何伯曼\NYou told me about a Lisa Hoberman.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.86,1:40:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她知道你会找出来. 你是个能干的警察\NShe knows you'd find out who Lisa is. You're a good cop.
