Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.89,1:41:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我也会这样做\NThat's what I'd do.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.35,1:41:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你干嘛改名？\NWhy'd you change your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.28,1:41:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我结婚了，他叫我贝丝\NI got married. He called me "Beth."
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.35,1:41:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他在沙林纳诊所执业\NHe was on staff at the clinic in Salinas.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.86,1:41:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}没待了多久\NDidn't last long.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.30,1:41:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}尼克 你以为我会杀人吗？\NDo you really think that I could kill someone?
