Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.17,1:41:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我又有什么动机杀尼尔森？\NAnd what about Nilsen? What motive would I have to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.87,1:41:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}把锁修好\N- You should get that lock fixed. - God...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.64,1:41:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她是个魔鬼！ 她聪明绝顶！\NShe's evil! She's brilliant!
