Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.66,1:42:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我曾去校园警局检举她\NI had to go to the campus police and file a report about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.30,1:42:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-你八成认为人是我杀的？\NI suppose you still think I kill people too?
