Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.95,1:43:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-凯瑟琳告诉我了. -她说的话能信吗\N- Catherine told me what was in it. - If she's telling you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.58,1:43:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}加斯，你还不明白吗？\NGus,don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.25,1:43:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}贝丝杀了强尼陷害凯瑟琳…\NIf Beth killed Johnny Boz to frame Catherine...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.25,1:43:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她怕别人知道柏克赖的往事！\Nshe wouldn't want anybody to know what happened in Berkeley!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.25,1:43:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}但被尼尔森发现了，使她有动机杀他\NBut Nilsen found out about it. That gives her the motive to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.56,1:43:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她怎么知道尼尔森发现了？\NHow did she know Nilsen found out, if it happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.59,1:43:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他是风纪组长，或许他去问她！\NHe probably asked her!
