Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.60,1:44:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我决定再给你一次机会\NI decided to give you a second chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.77,1:44:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-我想你. -我才刚走你就想我\N- I missed you. - I wasn't gone long enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.01,1:44:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你想我吗？\NDid you miss me?
