Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.83,1:44:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我已经看过了。- 是吗？\N- I've seen them before. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.10,1:44:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}不想再多看几眼吗？\NWell,you might not see them again.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.00,1:44:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我的书快完成了\NMy book's nearly finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.14,1:44:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}书中探长也快死了\NMy detective's almost dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.64,1:44:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我可以吸最后一根烟吗？\NSo I've got time for a last cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.28,1:44:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}事后再说\NAfterwards.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.59,1:45:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我明天早上要作些研究\NI've got to do some research tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.23,1:45:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}研究我很在行，我来帮你\NI'm good at research. I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.23,1:45:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}不用，谢了\NNo,thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.17,1:45:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你打算研究什么？嗯...\NWhat are you researching? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.10,1:45:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}替你的书找新的结局\Na new ending to your book.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.74,1:45:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}真的？怎么弄？\NOh,really? What's the twist?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.84,1:45:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}探长爱上不该爱的女人\NThe detective falls for the wrong girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.85,1:45:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}但他没死\NBut he doesn't die.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.28,1:45:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他结果怎样了？\NSo what happens to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.55,1:45:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他们不停疯狂的做爱…\NThey fuck like minks, raise rug rats...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.03,1:45:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}永远过着幸福的日子\Nand live happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.56,1:45:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}这不会畅销\NIt won't sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.60,1:45:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}为什么？\NWhy not?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.73,1:45:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}总得有人死掉\NSomebody has to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.74,1:45:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}为什么？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.64,1:46:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}天天有人死\NSomebody always does.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.60,1:46:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}早安，我找嘉纳大夫\NMorning. I'm looking for a Dr. Garner.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.86,1:46:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她已经不在这里工作了. 她好象去旧金山警局\NShe doesn't work here anymore. She's in San Francisco with the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.74,1:46:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我找的是他丈夫\NActually,I'm looking for her husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.30,1:46:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-他也在这里工作吧？ -约瑟夫嘉纳？\N- He works here too,doesn't he? - Dr. Joseph Garner?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.71,1:46:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你认识他？\N- She married? - You know him?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.61,1:46:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他五六年前就去世了\NHe died about five or six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.38,1:46:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-怎么死的？ -中弹身亡\N- How did he die? - He was shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.55,1:46:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}谢了\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.69,1:46:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他下班走路回家\NHe was walking home from work.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.59,1:46:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他住所离办公室很近\NHe only lived a couple of blocks from the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.93,1:46:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}有人开车经过射死她\NSomebody just drove by and shot him.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.69,1:46:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-是谋杀吗？ -点三八左轮手枪\N- What was the murder weapon? - Revolver,.38. Unrecovered.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.33,1:46:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-小心些. -有疑犯吗？\N- Watch yourself. - Were there any suspects?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.10,1:47:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}没有疑犯，没有动机. 无头悬案\NNo suspects,no motive. Unsolved.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.70,1:47:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他的太太有嫌疑吗？\NWas his wife ever a suspect?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.64,1:47:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}大约一年前也有人来问过\NOne of your guys was down here from Frisco a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.75,1:47:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他问了同样的问题\NHe was asking the same,exact thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.25,1:47:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}可以告诉我怎么回事吗？\NYou mind telling me what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.25,1:47:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}例行公事\NRoutine.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.85,1:47:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他是那样说的\NThat's exactly what he said.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.85,1:47:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}现在你又来说是"例行公事"\NNow I got two of you guys telling me it's "routine."
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.86,1:47:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}记得那家伙的名字吗？\NYou remember what the other guy's name was?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.36,1:47:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}不记得.我想不能确认\NNo. I can't really say that I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.70,1:47:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}尼尔森？\NNilsen?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.27,1:47:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}没错，正是\NYeah. That was it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.74,1:47:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-她曾经是疑犯吗？ -没有\N- So was she ever a suspect? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.58,1:47:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是有些闲言闲语\NThere was some talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.88,1:47:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}但一直没有证据\NBut it never panned out.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.01,1:47:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-说些什么？ -女人\N- What kind of talk? - Girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.22,1:47:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他有别的女人？\NHe had a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.55,1:47:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.69,1:47:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是她有女人\NShe did.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.36,1:47:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}如我所说，没有证据\NBut like I said, it never panned out.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.90,1:48:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-谢谢. -希望对你有帮助\N- Thank you. - Hope that helped you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.77,1:48:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是的，你帮了大忙\NYes,you did. You sure did.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.03,1:48:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我好想你\NI missed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.67,1:48:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我弄完我的研究\NI finished my research.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.84,1:48:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-我的书写完了. -故事是怎么结尾的呢？\N- I finished my book. - So how does it end?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.34,1:48:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我跟你说过了\NI told you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.58,1:48:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她杀了他\NShe kills him.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.98,1:48:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}再见，尼克\NGood-bye,Nick.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.79,1:49:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}再见？\NGood-bye?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.99,1:49:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}对，我的书写完了\NYeah. I finished my book.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.56,1:49:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你没听见吗？\NDidn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.73,1:49:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你的人物死了\NYour character's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.30,1:49:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}再见\NGood-bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.04,1:49:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你还在等什么，送花吗？\NWhat do you want,flowers?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.31,1:49:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我会给你一本我亲笔签的书\NI'll send you an autographed copy.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.61,1:49:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}这是干嘛，你在开什么玩笑\NWhat is this, some kind of joke?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.82,1:49:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我们在玩游戏吗？\NYou playing a game here?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.29,1:49:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}游戏结束了\NThe games are over.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.79,1:49:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你说得对\NYou were right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.56,1:49:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}它是本世纪最轰动的书，枪手\NIt was the fuck of the century, shooter.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.11,1:49:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我马上过去\NI'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.04,1:50:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}凯瑟琳楚梅大学一年级的室友\NCatherine Tramell's roommate, freshman year?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.04,1:50:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我刚接到她电话，她在奥克兰. 快上车\NI just got a call from her. She's in Oakland. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.32,1:50:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我找了他宿舍的朋友 找了一整天\NI've been phoning people from her dorm all day.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.35,1:50:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她大概知道我想联络到她\NShe must've heard I was trying to reach her.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.02,1:50:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她说她知道 凯瑟琳和丽莎何伯曼的底细\NSays she knows all about Catherine and Lisa Hoberman.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.59,1:50:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你还好吧？\NYou feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.96,1:50:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}还有一件事\NHere's something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.73,1:50:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}强尼巴兹的心理医生 在凡内士有个办公室\NJohnny Boz's psychiatrist has an office on Van Ness.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.13,1:50:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}猜猜看他和谁共用那办公室？\NGuess who he shares space with?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.00,1:50:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是伊丽莎白嘉纳大夫\NDr. Elizabeth Garner.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.71,1:51:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你究竟是怎么一回事？\NWhat in the hell's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.03,1:51:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我会在405号房\NI'll be in suite 405.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.06,1:51:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-你要上哪去？ -和你一起去呀\N- Where the hell you going? - I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.67,1:51:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你在休假\NYou're on leave,Hoss.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.60,1:51:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我不会去很久的\NIt ain't gonna take long.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.91,1:53:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}别动！\NFreeze!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.28,1:53:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你在这干嘛？\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.95,1:53:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}把你他妈的手举起来！\NPut your fucking hands up!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.89,1:53:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}加斯在我留言机上留言要会我\NI got a message to meet Gus here.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.89,1:54:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-他在哪里？ -别动，叫你别动！\N- Where is he? - Don't you move!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.16,1:54:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我知道你先生是怎么回事！ 你仍然是女同性恋吗，贝丝？\NI know about your husband! You still like girls,Beth?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.96,1:54:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-什么？ -把你的手从口袋里拿出来！\N- What? - Take you hands out of your pocket!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.66,1:54:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-把手拿出来！ -你是怎么了？\N- Take them out! - What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.97,1:54:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}把手拿出来！\NTake them out!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.22,1:54:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我爱你\NI loved you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.74,1:54:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}老天！\NOh,God!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.73,1:55:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你为什么会以为她有枪？\NWhat made you think she had a gun?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.80,1:55:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她跑到这里来干嘛？ 加斯在这做什么？\NWhat was she doing here? What was Gus doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.98,1:55:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}组长\NLieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.90,1:55:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我们的人\NOne of ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.11,1:56:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}老天\NJesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.81,1:56:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我们得去搜贝丝的住所\NWe'll have to check Beth's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.35,1:56:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}点三八口径的左轮枪\NThirty-eight caliber revolver.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.05,1:56:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}藏在书架上\NIn the bookcase, behind some books.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.26,1:56:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}查查它是不是杀尼尔森那把枪\NHave ballistics check it for Nilsen.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.56,1:56:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你最好进来看一下\NLieutenant. You better come in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.26,1:56:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我想大致是这样了\NI guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.24,1:57:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}绝对不是. 所有证据都不利于伊莉莎白嘉纳\NDefinitely not. We feel all the evidence points to Dr. Elizabeth Garner.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.92,1:57:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我们查过了，是她的尺寸没错\NWe checked. It's her size.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.98,1:57:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她在楼梯听到你声音 就把假发扔了\NShe probably heard you on the stairway and dumped this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.22,1:57:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}这里没有405\NThere's no suite 405.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.02,1:57:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}凯瑟琳楚梅的大一室友…\NCatherine Tramell's freshman roommate is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.02,1:57:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}两年前就因血癌去世了\NShe died of leukemia two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.03,1:57:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}-这是她的死亡证明. -莎莉娜如何？\N- Here's a fax of her death certificate. - What about Salinas?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.83,1:57:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是吗.等等，杰克！\NYeah,hold on. Jack!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.27,1:57:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}你去尼尔森办公室 找过嘉纳的档案没？\NDid you check Nilsen's office for any files on Beth Garner?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.57,1:57:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}柏克森那没有任何警方档案\NNo police report from Berkeley. Nothing at all about Salinas.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.27,1:57:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是我\NI'm back.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.14,1:57:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}太好了\NGreat.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.01,1:57:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}专家说那把点三八口径的左轮枪 与尼尔森的伤口吻合\NBallistics says the.38 we found in her apartment was used on Nilsen.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.35,1:57:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}没有登记\NNo registration. They're checking with Salinas.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.85,1:57:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}冰锥和巴兹那案子的凶器 既同牌又同型\NThe ice pick was the same brand and model as the Boz weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.85,1:57:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}查过了嘉纳住所和办公室的电话录音--\NChecked the tape machines at Dr. Garner's apartment and office...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.19,1:57:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}全部的办公室\Nboth here and the one on Van Ness.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.86,1:57:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}加斯没在任何地方留言\NThere's no message from Gus on any of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.29,1:57:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}她公寓里的录音机没有用过\NThe tape in her apartment was unused.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.36,1:58:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}强尼巴兹的心理医生说…\NJohnny Boz's psychiatrist says he thinks he remembers...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.16,1:58:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}他记得嘉纳和巴兹是一年前…\NDr. Garner and Boz meeting at a Christmas party at his house.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.57,1:58:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}在他家举行的圣诞派对中认识的\NA year ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.24,1:58:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}人心莫测，对不对？\NYou just can't tell about people, can you?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.98,1:58:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}即便是上过床的女人\NEven the ones you think you know inside and out.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.58,1:58:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}恭喜，柯伦\NCongratulations,Curran.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.91,1:59:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我听说了…\NI heard about what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:28.02,1:59:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}电视播了\NOn TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.93,1:59:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我不能对你用情\NI can't allow myself to care about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.94,1:59:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我不能对…\NI can't allow myself...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:51.77,1:59:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}任何人用情\Nto care.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:57.58,1:59:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我不想这么做的\NI don't want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:59.95,2:00:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我不想这么做的\NPlease. I don't want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.15,2:00:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我失去了所有的人\NI lose everybody.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.02,2:00:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我不想失去你\NI don't want to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.56,2:01:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我们现在怎么办，尼克？\NWhat do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.03,2:02:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}拼命做爱…\NFuck like minks...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.70,2:02:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}象老鼠一样快乐的活下去\Nraise rug rats and live happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:17.15,2:02:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我讨厌老鼠\NI hate rug rats.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.69,2:02:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}那拼命做爱好了，别想老鼠了…\NFuck like minks, forget the rug rats...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.69,2:02:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}快乐的生活下去\Nand live happily ever after.


